    "So you weren't left to your own devices as much.",
    "[INT 12]On the other hand, it might have been too much for some individuals: There were too many things.",
    "Every week there was something to do, you know.",
    "You didn't have time to swallow the information and were already moving on to other things... Maybe it would have taken a week or two between each chapter.",
    "What made it easier was to stop for a few weeks, then think about all the information."
  ],
